name: Write to modbus
Topic Setter
Response Message
func:
const button_name=msg.payload['address']
const value =msg.payload['value'][0]
const msgDict ={
    1000:"Dryer Forward",
    1001:"Dryer Reverse",
    1002:"Heater 1",
    1003:"Heater 2",
    1005:"SC1",
    1004:"SC2",
    1006:"Exhaust Fan",
    1007:"Cooling Fan",
    1008:"Vibrator",
}
const status = value===1?"turned ON":"turned OFF"
msg.payload={
    message:`${msgDict[button_name]} ${status} Successfully`
}
msg.topic='response'
return msg;
